{"tid":1671864,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"媽咪報告出咗 有腸化生","createTime":"2019-10-23T18:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T09:06:13.000Z","uid":304285,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"111ded9293619699b0601c5cb10649006395f372","tid":1671864,"uid":304285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T18:13:26.000Z","msg":"驗身報告出左 <br />\n有胃炎 腸化生 有幽門螺旋菌<br />\n話過三個月要去照多次胃鏡<br />\n我好擔心 <br />\n有冇過來人有經驗<br />\n可以教下我點做<br />\n我想好好地照顧媽咪同珍惜佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774375fb3407f101f67d872704db9787fdb16240","tid":1671864,"uid":267632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T18:18:06.000Z","msg":"多d陪佢傾計，支持佢<br />\n精神同意志都好重要"},{"pid":"95113e3492ad710dc87704c5462bce46a1a4ac0a","tid":1671864,"uid":304285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"774375fb3407f101f67d872704db9787fdb16240","tid":1671864,"uid":267632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T18:18:06.000Z","msg":"多d陪佢傾計，支持佢<br />\n精神同意志都好重要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T18:22:09.000Z","msg":"媽咪好多野都唔食得<br />\n醫生話唔可以再刺激個胃<br />\n想學煮飯煲湯水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb0ee90003b273dd07b9785069033a4c52b7a5c","tid":1671864,"uid":208931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T19:21:43.000Z","msg":"Will be alright 唔洗咁大壓力<br />\n覺得學下煮野食比媽媽孝順下佢幾好<br />\n絲打同auntie 加油"},{"pid":"e7a1b00d61e82c7e048fc4e341611c2835a8172d","tid":1671864,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"111ded9293619699b0601c5cb10649006395f372","tid":1671864,"uid":304285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T18:13:26.000Z","msg":"驗身報告出左 <br />\n有胃炎 腸化生 有幽門螺旋菌<br />\n話過三個月要去照多次胃鏡<br />\n我好擔心 <br />\n有冇過來人有經驗<br />\n可以教下我點做<br />\n我想好好地照顧媽咪同珍惜佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T20:00:05.000Z","msg":"腸化生，即腸上皮化生，是指在胃黏膜內出現了類似腸上皮的細胞。大部分患者當聽到了這個病理檢查發現都會顯得不明所以。但一知道有小部分腸化生會最終癌變，便會陷入恐懼中。<br />\n腸化生基本上可分為小腸型腸化及大腸型腸化，而其中大腸型不完全腸化與胃癌有密切關係。<br />\n胃黏膜腸上皮生化是最常見的胃黏膜病變，多見於慢性萎縮性胃炎和胃潰瘍。其中大多為小腸型化生，有炎症反應的性質，會隨着炎症的加重而加重，但一般很少發生癌變。研究亦指出若腸化生持續，患者患癌風險較同齡人士高10倍，同時約一成已確診腸化生的病人有機會於10年後患化成胃癌。<br />\n如果診斷為慢性萎縮性胃炎，患者需要每年作胃鏡檢查。如果發現早期癌變，患處可以經由胃鏡切除，如果癌變不能經胃鏡切除，外科手術切除後5年生存率亦可達95%以上，因此，定期胃鏡檢查是必須的。要減少患上胃癌，應戒煙、少吃鹹味重和醃製的食物，如有幽門螺旋菌感染，便要接受藥物治療。"},{"pid":"2d6bfab40f51ced45d564e558c49c70dc7d39df6","tid":1671864,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95113e3492ad710dc87704c5462bce46a1a4ac0a","tid":1671864,"uid":304285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"774375fb3407f101f67d872704db9787fdb16240","tid":1671864,"uid":267632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T18:18:06.000Z","msg":"多d陪佢傾計，支持佢<br />\n精神同意志都好重要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T18:22:09.000Z","msg":"媽咪好多野都唔食得<br />\n醫生話唔可以再刺激個胃<br />\n想學煮飯煲湯水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T20:01:53.000Z","msg":"煮清淡食物<br />\n睇黎唔太嚴重<br />\n未係真正生癌<br />\n唔好杞人憂天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIt is okay"},{"pid":"7b9622a6be77b663d9c55cfdfb32b372f5dbebec","tid":1671864,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T21:26:53.000Z","msg":"一定要戒糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n糖同炎症有關連"},{"pid":"b31c22cb5bc7ea77607d8db18e1b5a6a2177c740","tid":1671864,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b9622a6be77b663d9c55cfdfb32b372f5dbebec","tid":1671864,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T21:26:53.000Z","msg":"一定要戒糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n糖同炎症有關連"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:54:01.000Z","msg":"why?有咩科學根據？"},{"pid":"64bb786a0f4207b28eed004cb06d99e03f924c68","tid":1671864,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:57:59.000Z","msg":"岩岩話80 萬上到樓就話有事<br />\n厄保險? 有無咁橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06369f35e3e4dd4134628d1b6a633d52d0d0a20","tid":1671864,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64bb786a0f4207b28eed004cb06d99e03f924c68","tid":1671864,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:57:59.000Z","msg":"岩岩話80 萬上到樓就話有事<br />\n厄保險? 有無咁橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:01:42.000Z","msg":"你食屎大架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aeb7c297bc4b10d2a65a2a0ac87de025a837a5b","tid":1671864,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:04:46.000Z","msg":"要定期照胃鏡....<br />